{"tid":386784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：如黃之鋒獲美帝提名諾貝爾獎，我們要寫信去瑞典委員會投訴","createTime":"2017-09-04T07:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T11:16:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60ac3796386d0bfebaba4816fdc3b148012834ed","tid":386784,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155562309577225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155562309577225&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxDwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=323be59a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155562309577225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin 分享了 Ring Chan 的帖子。<br />\n3小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒的往績。如果他獲得美帝國提名諾貝爾獎，我們要寫信去瑞典的委員會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRing Chan<br />\n8小時 &middot;<br />\n我點解咁憎黃之鋒呢條仆街冚家剷？<br />\n<br />\n記得當日係旺角，佔領地俾中共黑社會數場，剷剩中間主帳幕，我地少數人守撚左成日，幾十人被幾百藍屍圍住，佢條仆街冚家剷，係金鐘叫人哋唔好來旺角支援，由得我哋死（如果唔係之後有市民自發增援，我哋死撚左啦！）⋯<br />\n<br />\n你老母呢筆數，我一定有機會同你計！<br />\n<br />\n有人比喻你喺香港馬丁路德金？<br />\n<br />\n我有機會就奬你9999千足純金！"},{"pid":"8944996d7e9afa3b0b3f7849874e090ca97c02c3","tid":386784,"uid":41737,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f48f710cb267ec8dc36135db23cde0c29e10db1f","tid":386784,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155561622872225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155561622872225&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxDwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1ea14a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155561622872225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin 分享了 Fafa Lee 的帖子。<br />\n11 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：<br />\n<br />\n港人奮鬥了三十年的民主運動，最終被親美的民主黨賣個清光，今日香港無法治無民主無人權，但有得到諾貝爾和平獎提名的政治犯，符合緬甸之類的第三世界的要求，可以等美國來接收香港了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>習近平總書記，中國共產黨縱容美方在香港搞政治二十年，中共黨中央出賣香港，得到美方多少金錢回報呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n一場猴子戲，在香港監獄上演。"},{"pid":"cbc79899c1e944a686aa35f4321667d7255ca995","tid":386784,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155562309577225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155562309577225&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxDwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=323be59a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155562309577225</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin 分享了 Ring Chan 的帖子。<br />\n3小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒的往績。如果他獲得美帝國提名諾貝爾獎，我們要寫信去瑞典的委員會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRing Chan<br />\n8小時 &middot;<br />\n我點解咁憎黃之鋒呢條仆街冚家剷？<br />\n<br />\n記得當日係旺角，佔領地俾中共黑社會數場，剷剩中間主帳幕，我地少數人守撚左成日，幾十人被幾百藍屍圍住，<span style=\"color: red;\">佢條仆街冚家剷，係金鐘叫人哋唔好來旺角支援，由得我哋死</span>（如果唔係之後有市民自發增援，我哋死撚左啦！）⋯<br />\n<br />\n你老母呢筆數，我一定有機會同你計！<br />\n<br />\n有人比喻你喺香港馬丁路德金？<br />\n<br />\n我有機會就奬你9999千足純金！</blockquote>\\<br />\n<br />\n嗰個係學聯喎，學民有份呼籲咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfs1958/photos/a.433111302871.207569.269056797871/10152478548937872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfs1958%2Fphotos%2Fa.433111302871.207569.269056797871%2F10152478548937872&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxDwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c11987a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfs1958/photos/a.433111302871.207569.269056797871/10152478548937872</a>"},{"pid":"d1c872a346c77330e48978524e1c6f8658ed605f","tid":386784,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"走開啦陳雲"},{"pid":"3816b6ceed710479bcf7350c2422d644e972a66b","tid":386784,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次又講得岩</blockquote><br />\n岩佢老母咩"},{"pid":"5ab372e51c229ab856ef7b71e9bc95a688f